* Esther Johnson, English friend of Jonathan Swift, known as &quot;Stella&quot;
* Stella Johnson (basketball), American basketball player
* Stella Johnson (photographer), American photographer</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q5401209" start="31" end="45" title="Esther Johnson" label="Esther Johnson"/>
